Version 0.5.0.02
* MaNGOS2 has received a lot of love, especially for the authentication and
  realm list server. It now is feature complete, and supports full account and
  realm management, and allows client connections from World of Warcraft client
  version 3.0.2 build 9056 in any client language.

Version 0.5.0.01
* Initial release of MaNGOS2, now following the principles of Agile Software
  development.
